All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AlertPopup
Static util class that is used for handling popup alerts.
CellGrid
Represents an abstract version of the game.
Controller
Controller interface with some basic events that may be used.
GameModel
Encapsulates and puts into context the functionality of CellGrid.
GameSceneController
Class that is responsible for acting upon the game scene.
ILoader
Loader Interface that is mostly used to catergorize loaders.
ISaveData
Interface used to categorize savable classes
ISaver
Saver interface for categorizing saver classes.
Main
Main class
MenuSceneController
Controller responsible for handling top-level actions from the Menu Scene.
MoveDirection
Enum for dictating movement directions in GameModel.
PrefFile
Class responsible for saving player preferences.
PrefLoader
Loader class for PrefFile objects.
PrefWriter
Saver class for PrefFile objects.
SaveFile
Class responsible for holding the seed of a game and the board state of a game when it is being saved.
SaveLoader
Loader class for loading SaveFile objects
SaveWriter
Saver class for SaveFile objects
SceneManager
Manages the properties of the scenes from a top-down perspective
ScoreFile
Class responsible for holding the hiScore of the game when it is being saved.
ScoreLoader
Loader class for ScoreFile objects.
ScoreWriter
Saver class for ScoreFile objects
SettingsController
Controller responsible for handling top-level actions in the Settings scene
